Others: Thomas Partey, Joseph Painstil, Kingsley Schindler, and Osman Ibrahim have withdrawn from the Ghana vs Sudan match due to injuries.
Thomas Partey is unable to join the Black Stars due to medical issues and will undergo further tests.
Joseph Painstil experienced pain in his hamstrings during their last game and will undergo an MRI on Monday.
Osman Ibrahim experienced pain in his calf muscles during their last game and is unavailable.
Kingsley Schindler is unable to join the Black Stars due to a medical emergency.
